ld @ Acme Engineering College- Sitapaila </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">3)<strong> Free and Open Source Software (FOSS) Nepal</strong></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Participant of Software Freedom Day 2013 @ Amrit Science College</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Participant of Open Data Day 2013</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Organizer &amp; Presenter of <a href="http://aoscacme.wordpress.com/2013/08/13/orientation-by-foss-nepal/"><span style="color: #0000ff;">SFD2014 Orientation</span></a> @ Acme Engineering College- Sitapaila </span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Organizer of <a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/open-data-day-2014-celebrated-in-nepal/"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Open Data Day 2014</span></a>, Kathmandu, Nepal</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Organizer of Software Freedom Day 2014 </span></li>\n</ul>\n<p align="left"><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">4) <strong>Mozilla Nepal</strong></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Participant of Mozilla South Asia Meet-up 2013, Kathmandu, Nepal</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Organizer of <a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/acme-mozilla-orentation/"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Acme Mozilla Orientation</span></a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Firefox Student Ambassador (FSA) and Club Lead of “<a href="https://wiki.mozilla.org/Acme_Firefox"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Acme Firefox</span></a>”</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Participant of <a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/mozilla-nepal-meet-up-iii/"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Mozilla Nepal Meet-up III</span></a></span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Presenter about <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="http://www.slideshare.net/nikeshba/firefox-student-ambassador-fsa"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Firefox Student Ambassador (FSA)</span></a> </span>@ Prime College</span></li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n	<li><span style="font-family: Arial,sans-serif;">Organizer &amp; Presenter at <a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/moz-maker-party-acme-engineering-college/"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Moz Maker Party</span> </a></span></li>\n	<li>My Open Badges Collection <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;"><a href="http://backpack.openbadges.org/backpack"><span style="color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;">http://backpack.openbadges.org/backpack</span></a></span></span></li>\n	<li>My Support Mozilla <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/user/931885"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Profile</span></a></span></li>\n	<li>My Mozillian <span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="https://mozillians.org/en-US/u/nikeshbalami/"><span style="color: #0000ff;">Account</span></a></span></li>\n</ul>', 'About Me', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '2-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-05-13 06:17:00', '2014-05-13 06:17:00', '', 2, 'http://neekes.com.np/home', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
