INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES(122, 1, '2013-12-26 11:15:01', '2013-12-26 11:15:01', '<a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/424475_541907715828245_1749586057_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-121" alt="424475_541907715828245_1749586057_n" src="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/424475_541907715828245_1749586057_n-300x115.jpg" width="500" height="200" /></a>\n\nWorking with <strong>FOSS Nepal Community</strong> was really cool but after hearing the name of <strong>Mozilla Nepal Community</strong> I was really socked. Different kinds of question was running through my mind. It was all started from "<strong>Mozilla South Asian Meet-up Kathmandu 2013</strong>" during <strong>Open Data Day Hackathon 2013</strong>. At that event I got an chance to know about Mozilla from closely but the more importantly I got chance to know about Firefox OS on that event.\n\n<a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/231047_554579147894435_279641439_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-123" alt="231047_554579147894435_279641439_n" src="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/231047_554579147894435_279641439_n-300x212.jpg" width="400" height="312" /></a>\n\nAfter attending that event is was interested to join Mozilla Community so, I started searching about Mozilla, Mozilla Nepal, Firefox OS etc. and after that I collect the name of Reps from Nepal and different contributor of Mozilla from Nepal and start adding them at different kinds of Social Sites. That''s helps me to be connected with them more easily and at that time I came to know about Firefox Student Ambassador (FSA) program. Then I joined that program and create on Firefox Club at my College named "<a href="https://wiki.mozilla.org/Acme_Firefox"><strong>Acme Firefox</strong></a>". After creating college club we decided to have one Orientation Program at our college and at the same time Mozilla Nepal Community did one Firefox Student Ambassador (FSA) Nepal Meetup-I which helps us to get communicate with others FSA from Nepal. We also did one Orientation Program at our college at 1st August 2013 and named it "Acme Mozilla Orientation"\nBlog post :<span style="color: #000080;"><a href="http://aoscacme.wordpress.com/about/"><span style="color: #000080;">http://aoscacme.wordpress.com/about/</span></a></span> and\n\n<span style="color: #000080;"><a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/acme-mozilla-orentation/"><span style="color: #000080;"> http://www.neekes.com.np/acme-mozilla-orentation/</span></a></span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe also celebrate Mozilla Nepal Anniversary together with lots of Fun and Mozilla Nepal Meetup-III was the most memorable one because I think that Meetup was quite successful. I also got an Firefox Student Ambassador (FSA) badg at 17 December 2013.\n\nBlog :<span style="color: #000080;"><a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/mozilla-nepal-meet-up-iii/"><span style="color: #000080;">http://www.neekes.com.np/mozilla-nepal-meet-up-iii/</span></a></span>\n\n<a href="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/1185830_642098865809129_971767163_n.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-124" alt="1185830_642098865809129_971767163_n" src="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/1185830_642098865809129_971767163_n-300x211.jpg" width="500" height="311" /></a>\n\n<a href="http://badg.us/en-US/badges/badge/Firefox-Student-Ambassador-Badge/awards/21701"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-125" alt="Screenshot from 2013-12-26 14:42:53" src="http://www.neekes.com.np/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Screenshot-from-2013-12-26-144253-300x176.png" width="500" height="376" /></a>', 'Journey with Mozilla Nepal Community', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '119-autosave-v1', '', '', '2013-12-26 11:15:01', '2013-12-26 11:15:01', '', 119, 'http://www.neekes.com.np/119-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
